BNY Mellon Trust Company (Cayman) Limited
 


overview

Deposit Guarantee
Locations



  


















Established in 1784, The Bank of New York Mellon (BNY Mellon) is 
an American investments company. BNY Mellon provides investment management, 
investment services and wealth management for institutions and individuals all over the world.BNY Mellon Trust Company (Cayman) Limited has Category B banking license number 
81016 issued by the Cayman Islands Monetary Authority. This type of 
license allows BNY Mellon Trust Company (Cayman) Limited to conduct banking and trustee operations 
with non-residents and domestic banking business with other Cayman Islands 
licenced entities.  




AddressCanella Court Suite 4206, 38 Market Street, Camana Bay, KY1-9006, Grand Cayman, Cayman IslandsP.O. Box766Phone345-769-6600 

Bank CategoryCategory B (Banking & Trust)Close Date31 December 2016  
 


 

