Deposit Guarantee



Deposit Guarantee




No


Deposit Guarantee Schemes compensate certain deposits 
held by depositors of a bank that becomes unable to meet its obligations.There is no deposit guarantee scheme in the Cayman Islands.In the case of BNY Mellon Trust Company (Cayman) Limited failure its depositors will no be paid out 
any compensation.




